Written evidence from Will O’Reilly [TOB05]
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Submission to the[bold] Home Affairs Committee inquiry into tobacco smuggling and the trade in illicit tobacco[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Will O'Reilly is a former Scotland Yard Detective Chief Inspector. Since November 2011, he has been conducting research on behalf of 
[normal]tobacco manufacturer 
[normal]Philip Morris International in order to gain intelligence and understanding of the illicit trade in cigarettes and other tobacco products across the United Kingdom and the Republic of Ireland.
